Polatovic's expression was contained in a letter to Iraqi
President Saddam Hussein, which was handed over to Iraqi Vice
President Taha Yassen Ramadhan by visiting Yugoslav Trade Minister
Vokovic Borislav, the INA said.
</P>
<P>
