<HEADLINE> URGENT  Canada's Top Court Rules on Quebec Separation </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
OTTAWA, August 20 (Xinhua) -- The Supreme Court of Canada ruled
here Thursday that Quebec can't separate from the country
unilaterally.
</P>
<P>
