million shares traded on the main board, industrial products
35.136 million shares, construction 37.429 million shares,
trading/services 133.419 million shares, infrastructure 2.090
million shares, finance 86.710 million shares, hotels 1.060
million shares, properties 28.857 million shares, plantation
10.366 million shares, mining 1.379 million shares, trusts 110,000
shares, closed/fund 94,000 shares and loans 19.452 million shares.
 
