<HEADLINE> Weather Forecast for Major Chinese Cities </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, August 20 (Xinhua) -- Weather forecast for 14 major
Chinese cities for the next 24 hours from 20:00 today to 20:00 on
August 21 issued by China's Central Meteorological Station at
17:00 today:
</P>
<P>
Beijing: min. 20 degrees C., max. 28 degrees C., clear to
overcast, calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Shenyang: min. 17 degrees C., max. 28 degrees C., clear, calm
to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Tianjin: min. 22 degrees C., max. 30 degrees C., clear to
cloudy, calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Xi'an: min. 19 degrees C., max. 24 degrees C., moderate rain to
drizzle, calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Chengdu: min. 23 degrees C., max. 29 degrees C., drizzle to
cloudy, calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Chongqing: min. 24 degrees C., max. 34 degrees C., cloudy, calm
to gentle breeze.
