<P>
A special award will be inaugurated to encourage outstanding
young organic chemists of Chinese origin around the world.
</P>
<P>
This is the fifth symposium in a series held every two years.
The four previous meetings were in Shanghai, Beijing, Taipei and Hong
Kong. 
</P>
</TEXT>
