of the exhibition: "The TDC is making consistent efforts to
support SMEs, who constitute the backbone of Hong Kong's economy."
</P>
<P>
He noted that Hong Kong still has economic advantages despite
the fallout from the Asia financial turmoil. These unique
advantages include close links with the mainland, competitive
service industry and extensive international business network, he
added.
</P>
<P>
The TDC Business InfoCenter, together with an affiliated SME
Service Center, was also opened here Thursday. Covering a floor
space of 1,300 square meters, the InfoCenter is the most
resourceful business information center in Hong Kong, with more
than 40,000 books and periodicals. The SME center is part of the
TDC's enhanced efforts to assist SMEs. 
</P>
