<TEXT>
<P>
KUALA LUMPUR, August 20 (Xinhua) -- Malaysian Prime Minister
Mahathir Mohamad Thursday called on the people to support the
drastic measures to be announced by the government for reviving
the economy.
</P>
<P>
Malaysians should support these measures as they are aimed at
reviving the economy, said Mahathir when addressing the 19th
general meeting of the Malay Contractors' Association of Malaysia
here.
</P>
<P>
