growth in Italy, the Audit Court said on Wednesday.
(Italy-Government Economy)
</P>
<P>
- - - -
</P>
<P>
LOS ANGELES -- Personal computer shipments in China and India
gained strong growth during the first quarter, although the
Asia-pacific region continued to falter.
</P>
<P>
The U.S. research firm International Data Corporation (IDC)
